channel.title: PI/Delta Objects
channel.description: Does anyone know how to remove the gates at Camelot castle on PI or Delta? If you do please tell me or if theirs a tutorial I missed please send. Thank you guys!

item.title: PI/Delta Objects
item.dc:creator: @Mariokillu Mariokillu
item.description:
@Mariokillu wrote:

For PI, Search

	public void loadCustomSpawns(Client c) {

Then below that you will see a bunch of codes like

		c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(OBJECT ID HERE, X COORD HERE, Y COORD HERE, 1, 10);

This one adds an object and if you scroll down a little, you will see

		if (c.heightLevel == 0)

Then you should start seeing code like this

			c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(-1, X COORD HERE, Y COORD HERE, 1, 10);

Just copy and paste that then add the coods of the item that you want deleted.

For Delta (Less explained since I did that for PI :3)

Open Client.java and search

public void Deleteobjects() {

Below that, there should be a lot of

 	       deletethatobject(X COORD, Y COORD);

Just copy and paste and replace the X COORD AND Y COORD with the coords of the object.

Hope this helps.
